message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper proposes a model for liver and liver lesion segmentation in CT volumes using fully convolutional networks. This involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques applied to medical imaging (cs.MED). Additionally, the use of neural networks (cs.NEURON) is a key aspect of the proposed method.
